(30, 'Russian court fines Twitter, Facebook, WhatsApp: report', 'The petition urged the HC to form a committee with technologists, educationists and lawyers to recommend BTRC', 4, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;A&amp;nbsp;Russian&amp;nbsp;court&amp;nbsp;on Thursday fined&amp;nbsp;Twitter&amp;nbsp;17 million roubles ($229,730), Facebook 15 million roubles and WhatsApp 4 million roubles over their refusal to localise user data as required by&amp;nbsp;Russian&amp;nbsp;law, Interfax news agency reported.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;We have already begun the due process and we are working on banning these harmful online games. We received a High-Court order regarding this yesterday (August 24) and have started preparing an official letter to be sent to the concerned authorities,&quot; says Subrata Roy, Vice Chairman, BTRC. &quot;We might not be able to ban all of them due to technical shortcomings, in that case, we will consult or outsource it to authorities who can.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;A list is also being prepared for harmful apps. We are currently evaluating and reviewing which apps are to be brought under this list,&quot; he added.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Earlier on August 16, the High Court directed the government to put a stop to all kinds of &quot;destructive&quot; online games and apps like PUBG and Free Fire for the next three months to &quot;save children and adolescents from moral and social degradation&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'pubg.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:02:01', NULL),
(31, 'Tamim left out of T20I central contract; Shakib reinstated in all formats', 'Tamim, however, was retained in the central contract for ODIs and Tests.', 5, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Bangladesh ODI skipper Tamim Iqbal was left out of the Bangladesh Cricket Board\'s (BCB) central contract list (from&amp;nbsp;May to December 2021) for T20Is after the left-hander had earlier today announced he will not be available for selection for the upcoming T20 World Cup in Facebook live from his official account.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Tamim, however, was retained in the central contract for ODIs and Tests.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Meanwhile, premier all-rounder Shakib Al Hasan, who was left out of the previous central contract (from January to December 2020) due to the all-rounder serving a year-long ban, has been reinstated contract for all three formats -- Tests, ODIs and T20Is.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;BCB, in their&amp;nbsp;11th meeting of the Board of Directors today, announced an extended central contract list which included a number of new faces.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;All-rounders Mahedi Hasan, Shamim Hossain, spinner Nasum Ahmed and wicket-keeper batsman Nurul Hasan Sohan were given only contracts for T20Is. Soumya Sarkar, who was included in white-ball only contract previously,&amp;nbsp;was&amp;nbsp;also only included in T20I contract after the BCB had made a list separating each format for the first time ever.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Batsman Mohammad Mithun and spinner Nayeem Hasan were the&amp;nbsp;two players excluded from the central contract list. Mithun was included in the red-ball contract and white-ball contract previously while Nayeem was only included in the red-ball contract in the previous list.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Tamim.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:05:03', NULL),
(32, 'BSEC dismisses board of Fareast Islami Life Insurance', 'The stock market regulator has dismissed the board of Fareast Islami Life Insurance to protect investors\' interest.', 3, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The stock market regulator has dismissed the board of Fareast Islami Life Insurance to protect investors\' interest.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The new board will restructure the top management of the company within six months, Bangladesh Securities and Exchange Commission (BSEC) said in a press release.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;It will be asked to bring back cash and assets and they will take legal action against the culprits who were involved in financial crime and money laundering, the BSEC said.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The new board will ensure that they have no conflict of interest with the insurer and follow insurance act, corporate governance code and securities law.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The BSEC appointed 10 independent directors for the new board.&lt;/p&gt;', 'fili.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:07:20', NULL),
(33, 'Apurba to tie the knot tomorrow', 'The intimate ceremony will take place tomorrow at a local community centre in Rajarbag.', 6, '&lt;p class=&quot;rtejustify&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Popular television actor Ziaul Faruq Apurba is set to tie the knot with an American expatriate girl named Shamma.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;rtejustify&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The news was confirmed to The Daily Star by Apurba himself.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;rtejustify&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The intimate ceremony will take place tomorrow at a local community centre in Rajarbag.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;rtejustify&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The &quot;Boro Chele&quot; famed actor had been married to actress Sadia Jahan Prova in 2010. He later tied the knot with Nazia Hasan Aditi in 2011. The former couple have a child named Ayash.&lt;/p&gt;', 'Apurba.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:09:10', NULL),
(34, 'China envoy visits Myanmar as new route to Indian Ocean opened', 'A spokesman for Myanmar\'s National Unity Government made up of opponents of military rule did not immediately respond to a request for comment on the Chinese visit.', 2, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;China\'s special envoy for Asian Affairs Sun Guoxiang visited Myanmar last week for talks with its military rulers, as a new route spanning the Southeast Asian nation opened up connecting Chinese trade flows to the Indian Ocean.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;As opposed to most Western countries that have condemned the army for ousting the elected government of Aung San Suu Kyi, China has taken a softer line and said its priorities are stability and not interfering in its neighbour.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;During his Aug. 21 to Aug. 28 visit, Sun met military ruler Min Aung Hlaing as well as foreign minister Wunna Maung Lwin and Minister for the Union Government Office Yar Pyae and &quot;exchanged views with them on the political landscape in Myanmar&quot;, China\'s foreign ministry spokesperson Wang Wenbin said on Tuesday.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;We will work together with the international community to play a constructive role in Myanmar\'s efforts to restore social stability and resume democratic transformation at an early date,&quot; Wang told a regular news briefing in Beijing, when asked about Sun\'s trip.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;China supported Myanmar working with the Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN) to implement a five-point consensus aimed at resolving the crisis and &quot;opposes undue external intervention&quot;, Wang said.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Opponents of Myanmar\'s junta have accused China of supporting February\'s military takeover that has sparked daily protests leading to hundreds of deaths and thousands displaced by fighting between the army and hastily formed militias.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Beijing has rejected such accusations and said it backs regional diplomacy on the crisis.&lt;/p&gt;', 'MY.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:11:04', NULL),
(35, 'Natural DIY solutions to prevent hair fall', 'It is imperative to understand your scalp type and choose a shampoo accordingly. A dry scalp obviously has different', 7, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;Hair fall is a phenomenon almost everyone faces in some point of life, irrespective of gender or age. Excluding the very few lucky ones, most people experience hair fall in either mild or extreme forms.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;A lot of factors lead to this. Heredity is considered one of the most prominent causes. Health conditions like hormonal imbalance, thyroid diseases, aging, certain types of medications and iron deficiency anaemia may often lead to hair loss. Other than medical reasons, lifestyle choice, emotional stress or trauma are also identified as some leading factors.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;While there are thousands of brands out there with their attractive chemical treatments, nothing can beat the magic of natural and DIY home remedies for hair fall.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;use mask. Egg masks made of egg, milk, lemon juice and olive oil can be an excellent choice. Eggs are enriched with proteins and vitamins and are great for hair growth.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Our good old friend banana is a hair fall saviour too as it is rich in potassium, antioxidants, natural oils, and vitamins. Mix ripe bananas, honey, coconut and olive oil and be witness to the tremendous results yourself. Curry leaves not only spice up your food but when mixed with coconut oil, can be an excellent hair fall remedy. The leaves stimulate hair growth and the coconut oil\'s penetrative properties enhances the mask\'s function. The curry leaves should be heated in coconut oil. Apply the oil once it has reached a warm temperature.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Green tea has great potential in promoting hair growth due to its high antioxidants and EGCG content. Mix green tea and egg yolk to prepare the mask.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;It goes without saying that a healthy lifestyle is the key ingredient for not only sound health but also for physical attributes like skin and hair. A diet rich in fruits, vegetables especially green leafy ones, nuts and seeds ensures hair growth. Eggs and omega-3 enriched fish promote healthy hair. Hydration is good news for your hair so make sure to drink plenty of water daily.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;section-media position-relative mb-20 float-right ml-20&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding: 0px; display: table; max-width: 15.625rem; margin-bottom: 20px !important; margin-left: 20px !important; float: right !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lg-gallery &quot; data-exthumbimage=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/small_1/public/images/2021/08/22/sis_hairstyle_20140602_0057.jpg?itok=sl-uw3xS&quot; data-src=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/very_big_1/public/images/2021/08/22/sis_hairstyle_20140602_0057.jpg?itok=No87Isfn&quot; data-sub-html=&quot;&lt;div class=\'lg-caption\'&gt;Photo: Sazzad Ibne Sayed&lt;/div&gt;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;open-popup&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; position: absolute; top: 0.625rem; right: 0.625rem; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); padding: 0.3125rem; animation: 2s ease 0s infinite normal none running pulse-zoom; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;expand&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-image: url(&amp;quot;/sites/all/themes/sloth/images/sprite_c91be62d7bce96377f39311463e01e5f.png&amp;quot;); background-position: 0px 0px; width: 37px; height: 37px; display: block; animation: 2s ease 0s infinite normal none running pulse-inner-zoom;&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;picture style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'hfall.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:13:00', NULL),
(36, 'Don\'t host content propagating militancy, pornography: Mustafa Jabbar to Facebook', 'He made the call during a virtual meeting with Facebook representatives yesterday, the minister told The Daily Star.', 4, '&lt;div class=&quot;section-content margin-lr pt-20 pb-20 clearfix&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 9.6875rem; padding-top: 0.625rem !important; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0.625rem !important; padding-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Posts and Telecommunications Minister Mustafa Jabbar has called on Facebook not to host content that propagates terrorism, militancy, sectarianism, sedition, pornography, and those that go against the socio-cultural values in Bangladesh.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;He made the call during a virtual meeting with Facebook representatives yesterday, the minister told The Daily Star.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;Facebook has said it will cooperate in all ways possible, he added.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;The meeting was attended by Sabhanaz Rashid Diya, Facebook\'s head of public policy for Bangladesh.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;Jabbar said Facebook has been asked to guard against the spread of falsehoods, rumours or propaganda from home and abroad that violate state, social and personal security and dignity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;He said Facebook has to host content in Bangladesh according to Bangladeshi laws.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-button-wrapper margin-lr text-center clearfix&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 9.6875rem; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;row align-center collapse app-link-wrapper&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: none; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;columns shrink small-full-width flex-container small-align-center&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; flex-grow: 0; flex-basis: auto; min-width: 0px; display: flex;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 'New Project.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:14:51', NULL),
(37, 'Bangladesh coach optimistic despite gulf in ranking', '&quot;I think there is a big difference in class and no space behind us. Kyrgyzstan and Palestine are strong teams and it will be tough games for us.', 5, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Bangladesh national team head coach Jamie Day is looking forward to producing positive results in Bishkek as the Three Nations Cup involving Palestine, Bangladesh and hosts Kyrgyzstan is all set to get underway tomorrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The curtain of the tournament will open through the match between hosts Kyrgyzstan and Palestine.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Bangladesh will take on Palestine and Kyrgyzstan on Sept 5 and 7 before playing a match against Kyrgyzstan U-23 team on Sept 9 as part of their preparation for October\'s SAFF Championship in Maldives. Jamie has taken this opportunity to apply the new playing formation as well as test some of his players, which includes two expatriate players. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;For us, it is a good preparation for the SAFF Championship we have in October and it\'s an opportunity to see the squad over three games in five days, so it is going to be tough for us playing against strong opponents but it will help us during the tournament in October,&quot; Jaime told the media at a pre-tournament conference in Bishkek today.&lt;/p&gt;', 'Football.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:16:51', NULL),
(38, 'Remittance slips to 6-month low', 'August was the third consecutive month that showed a downturn in remittance.', 3, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Remittance inflow has declined by 8 per cent year-on-year to $1.8 billion in August, lowest in six months due to money transfer through informal channels termed like hundi, increased, bankers said.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;August was the third consecutive month that showed a downturn in remittance.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;With the decline, the total inflow of remittances declined by 19 per cent year-on-year to $3.68 billion in the fiscal year 2021-22 from $4.56 billion in the same period a year ago, data from Bangladesh Bank showed.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Syed Mahbubur Rahman, managing director of Mutual Trust Bank, said the flow of remittances through formal channels decreased as the informal money transfer market increased.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Remittance hit the highest at around $25 billion in the last fiscal year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;We had an exceptional period last year, said another banker, who works at one of the largest remittances recipient banks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;He linked the drop in remittance inflow to declining jobs abroad compared to the Bank.&lt;/p&gt;', 'USD.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:19:30', NULL),
(39, 'Mafia: a web series and its inside stories', 'Renowned faces like Zahid Hasan, Anisur Rahman Milon, Shamol Mawla, Raha Tanha, Mou Khan, Orsha will be seen in the film. Mahiya Mahi, Misha Sawdagar, Emon and Anchal Ankhi have only recently been added to the cast.', 6, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Celebrated filmmaker Shaheen Sumon concocts love and underworld into his new venture &quot;Mafia&quot;, a web series which will soon available for viewing in 150 episodes. The movie is currently being shot at the Film Valley in Manikganj. Scripted by the director himself, the screenplay was done by Delwar Hossain Dil.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Renowned faces like Zahid Hasan, Anisur Rahman Milon, Shamol Mawla, Raha Tanha, Mou Khan, Orsha will be seen in the film.&amp;nbsp;Mahiya Mahi, Misha Sawdagar, Emon and Anchal Ankhi have only recently been added to the cast.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Director Shaheen Sumon told The Daily Star today that the story of &quot;Mafia&quot; revolves around Dhaka\'s underworld and its mafias. He claims a uniqueness in his series as he has combined the best of both movies and daily soaps, and they would do justice bringing out the essence and stories of the dark nook and crannies of Dhaka.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Mahiya Mahi said&amp;nbsp;that she has only started off with the shooting of &quot;Mafia&quot; after a long break, and that it gives her immense happiness working under a talented director like Shaheen Sumon.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;I have played the role of a swag 90\'s youth and this is the first time I am full-fledged sharing a screen with Mahi. I am hoping we are doing a good job and our viewers can expect to be entertained, well,&quot; says Emon.&lt;/p&gt;', 'mahi.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:21:26', NULL),
(40, 'With no evacuation flights, Afghans weigh risky overland trips to borders', 'It could be days or weeks before the negotiations between the Taliban, Qatar and Turkey on how to run the airport are finalised.', 2, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;As the last US&amp;nbsp;troops prepared to leave Afghanistan, Hussain, a US&amp;nbsp;passport holder who worked with the US&amp;nbsp;military, scrambled with his six daughters through Taliban checkpoints to the gates of Kabul airport for several days in a row, hoping to catch a flight to safety.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;He had called and emailed the US&amp;nbsp;Embassy for days without a response. Then a US soldier phoned him to say his only chance for a flight out was alone, without his daughters who are not US&amp;nbsp;citizens. Hussain\'s wife had died in July of COVID-19, and leaving would mean abandoning them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;On Monday night, the family stood in the throngs outside Kabul airport, listening to the roar of the final US&amp;nbsp;C-17 aircraft taking off, ending America\'s two decade-long military intervention in Afghanistan.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Hussain now is among an untold number in Afghanistan weighing a potentially hazardous overland journey, he told Reuters Tuesday, speaking through a translator.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;I hear from news and relatives that thousands are waiting at the Afghanistan borders with Pakistan and trying to get into Pakistan,&quot; said Hussain, who requested that his last name be withheld for security reasons. &quot;I do not know, should I go to Tajikistan,&quot; he wondered, worrying how he will be able to look after his daughters on the road if he goes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;With US&amp;nbsp;troops gone, US&amp;nbsp;evacuation flights over, and commercial fights avoiding Kabul\'s airport, which has no air traffic control, ad hoc private efforts to save thousands of Afghans unmoved by Taliban security assurances are increasingly focused on arranging safe passage across the land-locked country\'s borders.&lt;/p&gt;', 'Taliban.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:23:09', NULL),
(41, 'Bamboo shoot recipes from the Chittagong Hill Tracts', 'Take the shoots and make holes through it vertically by using a spoon and then stuffed with the sautéed stuffing. Set aside and heat a frying pan with oil in low-medium flame.', 7, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;It may once seem like the oddest of picks for a recipe, but the ever-rising popularity of bamboo shoots as a delicacy now makes fresh edible shoots available in the local market, especially during monsoon. Hill shoots are also available in the supermarket nowadays, not to mention online food pages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Modern research has revealed that bamboo shoots have many health benefits such as improving appetite and digestion, weight loss and curing few diseases as shoots may possibly have antibacterial and antiviral properties.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Traditionally, people like to cook and consume fresh or fermented shoots with sidol or dry fish paste gravy with other vegetables, and sometimes by stir frying with dried shrimp. Bamboo shoot meat curry is also a popular dish now. Bamboo shoots are versatile and allow pairings with a range of items like noodles, fried rice, soup to dal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline Medium&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;How to process —&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;To prepare fresh bamboo shoots, trim the fibrous outer layers and excess leaves starting from the base and working on towards its tip. Trim away any tough portion at the base but reserve the tender leaves, as they are edible. Then dice the shoot to your desired sizes. Dip the cubes in a bowl of cold water to avoid them turning brown. As raw shoots contain toxins, cook the shoots uncovered in boiling, salted water for about 20 minutes to detoxify them.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;section-media position-relative mb-20 clearfix&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); margin-bottom: 20px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lg-gallery &quot; data-exthumbimage=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/small_1/public/images/2021/08/30/food2.jpg?itok=Cs7-pF5l&quot; data-src=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/very_big_1/public/images/2021/08/30/food2.jpg?itok=p3ibB3g8&quot; data-sub-html=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;open-popup&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; position: absolute; top: 0.625rem; right: 0.625rem; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); padding: 0.3125rem; animation: 2s ease 0s infinite normal none running pulse-zoom;&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;expand&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; background-image: url(&amp;quot;/sites/all/themes/sloth/images/sprite_c91be62d7bce96377f39311463e01e5f.png&amp;quot;); background-position: 0px 0px; width: 37px; height: 37px; display: block; animation: 2s ease 0s infinite normal none running pulse-inner-zoom;&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;picture style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;source data-srcset=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/big_202/public/images/2021/08/30/food2.jpg?itok=mY3PpjXR&amp;amp;timestamp=1630341571 1x&quot; data-aspectratio=&quot;/&quot; media=&quot;(min-width: 1024px)&quot; srcset=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/big_202/public/images/2021/08/30/food2.jpg?itok=mY3PpjXR&amp;amp;timestamp=1630341571 1x&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot; lazyaspectratio lazyloaded&quot; data-aspectratio=&quot;&quot; data-srcset=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/big_202/public/images/2021/08/30/food2.jpg?itok=mY3PpjXR&amp;amp;timestamp=1630341571&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; srcset=&quot;https://assetsds.cdnedge.bluemix.net/sites/default/files/styles/big_202/public/images/2021/08/30/food2.jpg?itok=mY3PpjXR&amp;amp;timestamp=1630341571&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Food.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:25:19', NULL),
(42, 'Aston Martin\'s first SUV helps push up sales by more than 200%', 'The DBX entered production in July 2020 and has helped the company widen its appeal in a lucrative segment of the market which has proven profitable for its rivals.', 4, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Carmaker Aston Martin&amp;nbsp;(AML.L)&amp;nbsp;reported on Wednesday a 224% increase in sales to its dealers, boosted by its first sport-utility vehicle, the DBX, as losses fell in the first half of the year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The DBX 4x4, which first rolled off the production line just over a year ago, accounted for more than half of its 2,901 vehicles between January and June.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;&quot;Building on the success of DBX, our first SUV, we have since delivered two more new vehicles and with more exciting product launches to come we are well-positioned for growth,&quot; said Executive Chairman Lawrence Stroll.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Fictional agent James Bond\'s car brand of choice has had a tough time since floating in 2018, as it failed to meet expectations and burnt through cash, prompting it to bring in fresh investment from billionaire Stroll last year.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;The DBX entered production in July 2020 and has helped the company widen its appeal in a lucrative segment of the market which has proven profitable for its rivals.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.22222em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &amp;quot;Tiempos Headline&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);&quot;&gt;Its pretax loss fell from 227 million pounds in the first half of 2020 to 91 million pounds ($126 million), with the company saying trading was in line with expectations as it aims for 2021 volumes of around 6,000 vehicles.&lt;/p&gt;', 'Car.jpg', '103', '2021-09-01 18:26:55', NULL);
